      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHAIN DRIVE (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 24.50 beating Dernancourt. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. SUPER SEALANT (2) stuck on well last time to finish half a length back in second (20.09) at Healesville in a Grade 5 over 350m. Expected to be in the finish again. TIPSY TURTLE (5) turned in a plain performance last time when eighth at Healesville over 300m behind Path To Nirvana (17.31) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Expected to feature in the finish. HELLO COOPER (7) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can bounce back.",
